FBIS3-23293 "jptot011__l94109" JPRS-TOT-94-011-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 7 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA LEBANON Gunmen Blow Up Cars in Khirbat Slim NC0703075194 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 0715 GMT 7 Mar 94 NC0703075194 Beirut Voice of Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] The Israeli forces opened machine-gun fire on Mazra'at al-Hamra' and nearby villages overnight. There were no reports of casualties. Flares were fired over Kafr Tibnit, Zawtar al- Sharqiyah, Zawtar al-Gharbiyah, and the al-Litani River basin. Elsewhere, gunmen blew up cars belonging to Hasan Yasin and Muhammad Yasin in Khirbat Silm Town this morning. The Internal Security Forces immediately started investigating. The town of Khirbat Silm has been the scene of separate security incidents over recent weeks between the Amal Movement and Hizballah.
